Description:
ATTENTION: you need the workshop textures below for this map, or else the goals will appear black.

This is my first map that I started making last year for fun and just recently finished it. The map leans towards 1v1 or 2v2 game modes. I think this maps idea has potential but as you can tell from its aesthetics it stands as just a test map. Please try it out and have fun!

UPDATE: 
This map should now be fixed with new and improved boost pads and less texture errors :)
